Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've sometimes seen strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,My my, we didn't catch a thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:51.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}[ Akebi: An edible fruit found in shrubs. ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go pick some akebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Did you see a human child just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,The grandchild of Natsume Reiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,the one with the Book of Friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}should{\i0} have run this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Lie to me and I'll eat you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where did he run?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,He looked yummy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,A human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,The things I see are probably what other people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,call "youkai", or monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.31,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Name of {\c&H84648A&}a{\c} Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.31,title,,0,0,0,,The Name of {\c&H035A09&}a{\c} Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,My grandmother left me a book: "The Book of Friends".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,My grandmother possessed strong spiritual powers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,and challenged every youkai she met to a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,When she defeated them, she had them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,write their names in this book
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,to prove that they would obey her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,The Book of Friends is a set of contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,Call the names within
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,and the name holder cannot disobey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ever since I got it, I've spent my days running from youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to catch my breath first before I go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,A teacup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's it doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, come out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't go hiding under people's houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,T-Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Shopping took longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:52.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Um, I thought I saw a rat. Probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,We have a cat at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,My, you've dirt all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:12.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}[ Sukiyaki: A Japanese hotpot/steamboat dish. ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh right, we're having sukiyaki today, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,I need to be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,not to do anything that might seem weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,If that was indeed a rat, we should buy some rat traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, I've made a mistake, it was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:30.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was just one of our neighbor's puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun, a second round perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,I lost my parents when I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,and my relatives passed me around until finally
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,the Fujiwaras took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,This home is very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's called a Kagejawan (shadow cup).
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's lived below the house for about two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's been there two weeks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're supposed to be guarding the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Calm down, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,Go get me another, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,When an exceptionally well-made teacup
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,breaks and is thrown out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,sometimes it absorbs the power of the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,and becomes a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then it takes up residence
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,under old houses so it can be near people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,So it can be near people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,I hear that sometimes when a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,is about to visit the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,it will run around to warn people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,and sometimes on a whim
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,it will sacrifice itself to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,So, it's harmless?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,Once it gets bored, it'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,And I'm not a "guard",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,it's just that I get the Book of Friends after you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,so I'm protecting you from youkai that come to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume-sama, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've come to ask for my name back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ever since I inherited the Book of Friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:06.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've returned the names of the youkai within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,First I bring up an image of them in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,and recite...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,"That which shields me, reveal thy name."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,To release their names, you need the saliva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,and breath of someone of the same
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,bloodline as Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,When I return their names, I get really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,There goes another page out of the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,They come without asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,and then they leave just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,Will I ever become strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,to not have my life ruled by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,It sounds like footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,I hear that sometimes when a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:00.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,is about to visit the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,it will run around to warn people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's running around already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.00,classsign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628.1,536.1)\be2\frx-5\fax0.2\frz350.2}Year 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hClass 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,some kind of disaster is going to visit the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,Finally having troubles with love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,You must be up reading those "H" books, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's going on with Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,What? That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've made friends since I came to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard that my grandmother, Reiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,didn't have many human friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,I think that's why she picked fights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,with all the youkai she met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,My staff, my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Your staff is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can see me, can't you, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,This is bad, she's a youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,What strong power you have, child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can't see well, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Help this old woman out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:46.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,I borrowed a mirror from a powerful youkai a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't know her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,but the other youkai feared her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,and said she brought with her great disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:58.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Someone of your power should be able to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:08:59.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,Since you can see youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:11.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,then you should also know the consequences of refusing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I don't want to be in any part of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,If I get involved with a youkai that brings disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,I might bring disaster to the Fujiwara family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,My poor child, a word of advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you don't help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you don't come, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Trouble. Some weird youkai-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,You've been cursed, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Who dares lay a hand on my prey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,An old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:56.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,An old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sounds scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:00.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:07.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something the old lady said bothered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,The Kagejawan is running...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,Did I bring in the disaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's not going to bloom this year either?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,If it withers away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll be sad and have nothing to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.11,natsume,,0,0,0,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,Or was it that youkai's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,You said you'd wait till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:55.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,I finally met somebody who could find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,It would be a waste if you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm an impatient old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,Or will you not help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,So don't come into this house!
