Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.03,titlename-blur,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1214,219)\p1\blur20}m 0 0 s 1350 0 1350 150 0 150 c
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that old lady somebody so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,even you couldn't get rid of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,My guess is that she's a divine being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,that once had a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'd be all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,but if somebody less powerful touched her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,they'd probably be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,She's that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:41.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,In this age most gods like that are sick or weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,She looks like she can barely see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Go with her for a bit and just take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,So someone with less power can't even get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that why she's so glad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,she found a human who can see youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,A god who can be with neither youkai nor humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Reiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,This way, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,A flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,It smells good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,I put it in my hair to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,It does smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see... it does, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,This way, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,I met her in the forest up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me "child," please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,Since she doesn't spend much of her time with youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,she doesn't know I'm the one with the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's easy to get lost in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's somewhere over here that I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,What kind of youkai was her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,She, who was known to bring disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:04.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see well, but she was quite small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,Small...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,If we go all out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,maybe Sensei and I could take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,Didn't the old lady said she borrowed a mirror from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even though it was so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see... so that's what bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't have many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:28.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,There was an old cherry blossom tree near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,but it was possessed by a stubborn evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,An old tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,so that's what that dream was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,So it started to wither,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,and to get rid of it I needed a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,I was looking for a mirror and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,I came upon somebody holding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought I would steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,But I was defeated and knocked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Some god, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,But when I said I really needed the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,she gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even though everyone avoided her in fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,I guess she wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:09.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,But the other youkai were terrified of her and kept their distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:15.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,She said so herself, that she would bring disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:18.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't like humans much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,After I got the mirror, I tried to get rid of the spirit, but was unsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,So I went back to return the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:31.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,But she said she didn't want to see the mirror, and didn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,From then on, we would meet occasionally and chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.10,natsume,,0,0,0,,When I looked at her this close,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,she had a scar somewhere here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Though the youkai disliked her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,that scar seemed to be the result of an attack by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:51.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,I found her kind of cute, and invited her to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,But when she saw my shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,she seemed a little disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not long after, I told her my story,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,and she got rid of the spirit in the tree for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,See, this flower is from that tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:14.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, why is it that you smell so much like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,And when I look at you up close, you look kind of like her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Please show me that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:28.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've been sensing the heat emanating from the Book of Friends for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Old lady, the person you're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've finally found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume, of the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,This time you won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's the one from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,My left shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, your shoulder's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought it ate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, it doesn't seem to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here I thought that lump of fur there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.96,natsume,,0,0,0,,was supposed to be your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,Useless, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,What?! Wasn't it I who got rid of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it's all because Natsume was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,I need to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's different now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,at least to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't care if he loses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,an arm or a leg or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,as long as the Book of Friends is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume, the Book of Friends is safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Your name is in the Book of Friends, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,The Book of Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,I did write my name on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:10.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, she stopped coming for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,Old lady, there is no point to still be looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:19.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,She was probably my grandmother, Natsume Reiko -- a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:26.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,That which shields me, reveal thy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,I return your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,Please take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,Aokuchinashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,How infuriating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:45.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,The flowers of that tree were my one pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,A mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,If only I had a mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard she brings disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,She's said to be more terrible than a demon god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,We should stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Lets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,What? The one who smells like a child of man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,I've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,My staff... my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,Your staff is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,Would you give me your mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:36.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,The one friend I have needs a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,They sell mirrors at the store up the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,I just need to borrow it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just looking at it through the mirror isn't going to cure my wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.78,natsume,,0,0,0,,What? You're hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're a strange person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here's your mirror back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,I hate looking into the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,You've been coming here often lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,I want to go further away, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,A place nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,Would you come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's a tree, though almost withered away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,it has very beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,A shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,And there's the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Somebody who would actually talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're a youkai, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:10.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then have a match with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll do anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can even eat me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,But if I win, you'll write your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:27.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,After losing the match, I wrote my name on a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,She never did give me her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see... so it's Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Her name was Natsume Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,So, Reiko is no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,Please keep that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,You've helped me greatly, grandson of Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,Go down that path and you'll return back to civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Straight down that path!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,Just like the old lady thought Reiko was a youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,Reiko thought the old lady was human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,How happy she must've been when she thought
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,she had a human friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:23.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,This incident couldn't be the reason why Reiko started to hate youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,The flowers the old lady talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is the tree Reiko banished the spirit from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,Crazy woman, she was just a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,She got rid of the evil spirit from the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.07,natsume,,0,0,0,,after she learned that the old lady was a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Touko-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,There's a broken tea cup I've never seen before here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,See, whose is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and sometimes on a whim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:07.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will sacrifice itself to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,They come without asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,and then they leave just the same.
